sentences: Dragi Šestić (born 14 May 1966) is a Bosnian music producer, sound engineer, director of music video clips and record label owner.
In 1998 he founded the first Bosnian World Music band, Mostar Sevdah Reunion.
His work can be found on many World Music compilations, but most of it is on his record label Snail Records, founded in 2002.
